Revision history for Perl extension Win32::Daemon::Simple.

0.1.0  Thu Oct 31 19:28 2002 (CET)
	- original version

0.1.2  Tue Nov 5 14:46 2002 (CET)
	- a few small tuneups
	- changed the way param_modify handlers report invalid data
	- added -default and -defaultPARAM options

0.1.3  Tue Nov 5 16:04 2002 (CET)
	- fixed ticking

0.2.2	Wed Feb 26, 2003 (CET)
	- changed the format of datestamps
	- added more commandline options

0.2.5 Mon Apr 7, 2003
	- added support for multiple services running the same script/executable
	- added service options setting (-service:user, -service:interactive, ...)
	- the service prints the old value plus the error message if a param_modify=> handler dies
	- fixed a bug causing incorrect DoEvents() handler to be called when the service is unpaused

0.2.6 Sun Mar 14, 2004
	- added a check for Win32::Registry 0.08 or my patch
